parameters: That lift is our way down into The Underground.
Whoa there, I don't remember saying you could leave...
Come on, why so hostile?\! I just came to check on my friends.
We're doing fine.\! So you can leave now.
Are you really?\! I can't help but notice that you still look really flustered.
You're confused.\! And you don't know why.
Go on...\! Tell us what's going on in that head of yours.
Quit playing games.\! Let us leave without any trouble.
You're one to talk.\! It's too late for that.
You know who I am \n[1].\! Go on.\! Say it!
Fine.\! If you won't remember on your own...
Maybe I can give you a jump start!
What's the matter \n[1]?\! You're slowing down.
*tsk*\! You still haven't got what it takes.
Take lift down to The Underground?
